# Python

- **pixi project:** `pixi install`, `pixi run …`, `pixi add …`
- **uv project:** `uv sync`, `uv run …`, `uv add …`
- Do not use bare `python` or ad-hoc `pip install` when a project manager exists.
- Docs: Context7 MCP or official pixi/uv docs — not invented wrapper commands.
- Type hints on public functions; run project linters when present.
- Jupyter: `canfar-lab-kernel-register` after env resume when paths change.
